==分類==
圭亞那響尾蛇原先被命名為''C. d. dryinus''<ref name="McD99">{{Cite book en|author=McDiarmid RW, Campbell JA, Touré T|year=1999|title=Snake Species of the World: A Taxonomic and Geographic Reference, vol. 1. Herpetologists' League|pages=511 pp|isbn=1-893777-00-6}}</ref>，現已被認為是指名[[亞種|亞種]]的[[異名|異名]]。正確來說，以往南美響尾蛇的指名亞種後來成為了''C. simus''的指名亞種，而圭亞那響尾蛇則改為南美響尾蛇的指名亞種。<ref name="C&L04"/>''C. d. collilineatus''及''C. d. cascavella''都被認為是''C. d. terrificus''的異名。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Wüster W, Ferguson JE, Quijada-Mascareñas JA, Pook CE, Salomão MG, Thorpe RS|year=2005|title=Tracing an invasion: landbridges, refugia and the phylogeography of the Neotropical rattlesnake (Serpentes: Viperidae: ''Crotalus durissus'')|journal=Molecular Ecology|volume=14|pages=1095-1108|url=http://biology.bangor.ac.uk/~bss166/Publications/2005_Crotalus_durissus.pdf PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061225015653/http://biology.bangor.ac.uk/%7Ebss166/Publications/2005_Crotalus_durissus.pdf|archivedate=2006-12-25|access-date=2020-12-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Wüster W, Ferguson JE, Quijada-Mascareñas JA, Pook CE, Salomão MG, Thorpe RS|year=2005|title=No rattlesnakes in the rainforests: reply to Gosling and Bush|journal=Molecular Ecology|volume=14|pages=3619-3621|url=http://biology.bangor.ac.uk/~bss166/Publications/2005_Gosling_Bush_reply.pdf PDF|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061227002053/http://biology.bangor.ac.uk/~bss166/Publications/2005_Gosling_Bush_reply.pdf|archivedate=2006-12-27|access-date=2020-12-29}}</ref>

